These are some of the bounties:TWITTER: UP TO 400 DELTAC/weekBLOG / ARTICLE: UP TO 800 DELTACYOUTUBE VIDEO: UP TO 2,700 DELTACBITCOINTALK CAMPAIGN: UP TO 400 DELTAC/weekCheck more details about the Airdrop here.DeltaCryptos ICO Main thread
